46:34.480 --> 46:41.800
We are moving through a massive phase transition from an era of signal preservation to an era of latent communication.

46:41.800 --> 46:47.620
We are building a universal mathematical topology where all media is connected.

46:48.500 --> 46:55.160
But the epistemic closure of this system means it inherently embeds a specific worldview.

46:55.380 --> 46:58.920
