47:25.400 --> 47:31.500
It will literally erase cultural nuances and physical idiosyncrasies for the sake of mathematical efficiency.

47:31.500 --> 47:39.000
How do we prevent this generative ecology from collapsing into a homogenized hallucination?

47:39.000 --> 47:41.000
The only solution Flyxion proposed...

47:41.800 --> 47:44.800
