48:23.600 --> 48:25.600
The dynamics are exactly the same.

48:25.600 --> 48:29.600
The mathematical dynamics are identical, but the constraints are vastly different.

48:29.600 --> 48:37.600
Human semantic drift in ASL is heavily anchored by the physical need to actually communicate complex, nuanced emotional truths...

48:37.600 --> 48:40.600
