48:40.600 --> 48:43.600
The friction of reality grounds the drift.

48:43.600 --> 48:50.600
But machine drift, left unchecked in a frictionless digital loop, has no anchor.

48:50.600 --> 48:55.600
It optimizes purely for algorithmic efficiency, not for the preservation of the human soul.

48:55.600 --> 49:01.600
It could permanently erase the chaotic nuances of the physical world from our digital record.

49:01.600 --> 49:06.600
This has been an incredibly dense paradigm-shifting hour.

49:06.600 --> 49:08.600
