49:41.600 --> 49:48.600
The duality of prediction and compression proves that algorithms might comprehend physics to encode them efficiently.

49:48.600 --> 49:57.600
We explored the deep categorical mathematics of nearest prototype projections, gauge fixing, and sheaf theoretic constraints...

